    "description": "Grace Stowel custom API endpoints including health checks and custom store/admin routes. These endpoints extend the standard Medusa API with application-specific functionality.\n\n## Endpoints Overview\n\n- **Health Check**: System health monitoring endpoint for deployment verification\n- **Store Custom**: Custom storefront-facing endpoints\n- **Admin Custom**: Custom admin endpoints (requires authentication)",
